thread.title: BRIEF-Beijing Tensyn Digital Marketing Technology Joint Stock to swing to profit in FY 2017

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Beijing Tensyn Digital Marketing Technology Joint Stock to swing to profit in FY 2017

organizations.name: tensyn digital marketing technology joint stock
beijing tensyn digital marketing technology joint stock co

text:
Feb 1(Reuters) - Beijing Tensyn Digital Marketing Technology Joint Stock Co
* Sees to swing to net profit at 5 million yuan to 10 million yuan in FY 2017 versus net loss at 265.8 million yuan year ago
* Says increased sales and cost control are the main reasons for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/iauiJc
